{"tid":1802583,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"歷史政治類台灣Youtuber講建制派同民主派","createTime":"2019-12-29T14:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T15:08:37.000Z","uid":239674,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35032a69cf72e1bbe8320656c270e4cbcba94024","tid":1802583,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:43:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8sJMLzCJEc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm8sJMLzCJEc&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK98bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=90194143\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m8sJMLzCJEc</a><br />\n<br />\n大部分民主派 一輩子只想座在議席上 領受到優渥的薪水和社會地位.....<br />\n有睇開youtube既手足麻煩subs佢支持吓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ:點解要支持佢?<br />\nA:佢利用佢youtube 394k subs既影響力同埋中立既角度向台灣人同埋識聽國語既星馬人解釋香港發生緊咩事，真係好值得支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過隔離睇吓隻达狗，身為生為香港人，都奶人民幣奶撚到啞撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一直有冇關注埋1月1號呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d739a0d235797c13300ea0768ebc5616804ecea","tid":1802583,"uid":239674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:45:20.000Z","msg":"PISH"},{"pid":"44a45a9c822e8079070725e85a9f9c42a78dae77","tid":1802583,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:45:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK98bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=33181eb5\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</